{"parentUuid":null,"isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"D:\\yyc\\claude","sessionId":"9090f986-3e68-466e-84dd-8a359bb7877a","version":"2.1.55","gitBranch":"HEAD","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"我要在另一台电脑上安装claude code，我有智普的apikey和urlbase，我要让claude像本机一样，直接从智普的apikey和urlbse启动，请写出命令"},"uuid":"55ae438e-8422-45a5-8bc6-5d74e13ae5a8","timestamp":"2026-02-25T05:30:21.744Z","todos":[],"permissionMode":"default"}
{"parentUuid":"55ae438e-8422-45a5-8bc6-5d74e13ae5a8","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"D:\\yyc\\claude","sessionId":"9090f986-3e68-466e-84dd-8a359bb7877a","version":"2.1.55","gitBranch":"HEAD","message":{"id":"msg_20260225133028d3ade825effd4299","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"glm-4.7","content":[{"type":"text","text":"您可以使用以下命令直接启动 Claude Code 并配置智谱 API：\n\n```bash\n# 使用 API Key 启动（推荐方式）\nANTHROPIC_API_KEY=你的智普_API_KEY ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=你的智普_URL_BASE npx -y @anthropic-ai/claude-code\n```\n\n**完整示例：**\n```bash\nANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://open.bigmodel.cn/api/paas/v4/ npx -y @anthropic-ai/claude-code\n```\n\n---\n\n**如果要永久保存配置，可以创建或编辑环境变量：**\n\n```bash\n# Windows PowerShell - 设置用户环境变量（永久生效）\nsetx ANTHROPIC_API_KEY \"你的智普_API_KEY\"\nsetx ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL \"你的智普_URL_BASE\"\n\n# 设置完成后，以后直接运行以下命令即可\nnpx -y @anthropic-ai/claude-code\n```\n\n```bash\n# Windows CMD - 设置用户环境变量（永久生效）\nsetx ANTHROPIC_API_KEY \"你的智普_API_KEY\"\nsetx ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL \"你的智普_URL_BASE\"\n\n# 设置完成后，以后直接运行以下命令即可\nnpx -y @anthropic-ai/claude-code\n```\n\n---\n\n**注意：** 智谱 AI 的 `ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL` 通常是：\n- `https://open.bigmodel.cn/api/paas/v4/` (新版)\n- 或 `https://open.bigmodel.cn/api/paas/v4/`\n\n请根据智谱官方文档确认正确的 URL。"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3403,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":14336,"output_tokens":351,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"2fee9898-7e5d-4230-8a0d-41f7ed6bdaea","timestamp":"2026-02-25T05:30:35.599Z"}
