{"parentUuid":"2fee9898-7e5d-4230-8a0d-41f7ed6bdaea","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"D:\\yyc\\claude","sessionId":"9090f986-3e68-466e-84dd-8a359bb7877a","version":"2.1.55","gitBranch":"HEAD","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"还是无法通过智普Unable to connect to Anthropic services\n\n Failed to connect to api.anthropic.com: ERR_BAD_REQUEST\n\n Please check your internet connection and network settings.\n\n Note: Claude Code might not be available in your country. Check supported countries at\n https://anthropic.com/supported-countries"},"uuid":"03d5aaa9-4826-4e5b-975b-83eedc4185e8","timestamp":"2026-02-25T05:37:22.483Z","todos":[],"permissionMode":"default"}
{"parentUuid":"03d5aaa9-4826-4e5b-975b-83eedc4185e8","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"D:\\yyc\\claude","sessionId":"9090f986-3e68-466e-84dd-8a359bb7877a","version":"2.1.55","gitBranch":"HEAD","message":{"id":"msg_20260225133725b1555826e7e9482f","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"glm-4.7","content":[{"type":"text","text":"看起来环境变量没有生效。让我们尝试其他方法：\n\n**方法 1：在同一行命令中设置环境变量（确保生效）**\n\n```bash\n# PowerShell\n$env:ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=\"你的智普_API_KEY\"; $env:ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=\"你的智普_URL_BASE\"; npx -y @anthropic-ai/claude-code\n```\n\n```bash\n# CMD\nset ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=你的智普_API_KEY && set ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=你的智普_URL_BASE && npx -y @anthropic-ai/claude-code\n```\n\n---\n\n**方法 2：创建 .env 文件（推荐）**\n\n在当前目录创建 `.env` 文件：\n\n```bash\n# 创建 .env 文件\necho ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=你的智普_API_KEY > .env\necho ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=你的智谱_URL_BASE >> .env\n```\n\n然后运行：\n```bash\nnpx -y @anthropic-ai/claude-code\n```\n\n---\n\n**方法 3：使用配置文件**\n\n在用户目录创建配置文件：\n\n```bash\n# Windows 配置文件路径\n# C:\\Users\\你的用户名\\.anthropic\\config.json\n```\n\n配置文件内容：\n```json\n{\n  \"apiKey\": \"你的智普_API_KEY\",\n  \"baseURL\": \"你的智普_URL_BASE\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n**方法 4：直接在命令行中传递**\n\n```bash\n# Windows PowerShell\nnpx -y @anthropic-ai/claude-code --api-key \"你的智普_API_KEY\" --api-url \"你的智普_URL_BASE\"\n```\n\n---\n\n**请告诉我：**\n1. 您使用的是什么终端？\n2. 智谱的 `BASE_URL` 具体是什么？\n\n这样我可以给您更精确的命令。"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":106,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":18048,"output_tokens":396,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"ac708521-10f0-474e-8897-7664195afccf","timestamp":"2026-02-25T05:37:41.664Z"}
