{"parentUuid":"ac708521-10f0-474e-8897-7664195afccf","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"D:\\yyc\\claude","sessionId":"9090f986-3e68-466e-84dd-8a359bb7877a","version":"2.1.55","gitBranch":"HEAD","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"PS C:\\Windows\\system32> npx -y @anthropic-ai/claude-code\nnpx : 无法加载文件 D:\\Node.js\\npx.ps1，因为在此系统上禁止运行脚本。有关详细信息，请参阅 https:/go.microsoft.com/fwlink/\n?LinkID=135170 中的 about_Execution_Policies。\n所在位置 行:1 字符: 1\n+ npx -y @anthropic-ai/claude-code\n+ ~~~\n    + CategoryInfo          : SecurityError: (:) []，PSSecurityException\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : UnauthorizedAccess"},"uuid":"f6288d61-8c41-473d-9966-e3a615e8e826","timestamp":"2026-02-25T05:47:17.976Z","todos":[],"permissionMode":"default"}
{"parentUuid":"f6288d61-8c41-473d-9966-e3a615e8e826","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"D:\\yyc\\claude","sessionId":"9090f986-3e68-466e-84dd-8a359bb7877a","version":"2.1.55","gitBranch":"HEAD","message":{"id":"msg_20260225134720dba04bd4dc324376","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"glm-4.7","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这是 PowerShell 的执行策略限制。解决方法：\n\n**临时解决（推荐，仅当前会话生效）：**\n\n```powershell\nSet-ExecutionPolicy -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope Process\nnpx -y @anthropic-ai/claude-code\n```\n\n---\n\n**一次性的完整命令：**\n\n```powershell\nSet-ExecutionPolicy -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope Process; $env:ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=\"你的智普_API_KEY\"; $env:ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=\"你的智普_URL_BASE\"; npx -y @anthropic-ai/claude-code\n```\n\n---\n\n**永久解决（以管理员身份运行 PowerShell）：**\n\n```powershell\nSet-ExecutionPolicy -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope CurrentUser\n```\n\n---\n\n**或者直接使用 cmd 而不是 PowerShell：**\n\n按 `Win + R`，输入 `cmd`，然后：\n\n```cmd\nset ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=你的智普_API_KEY && set ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=你的智普_URL_BASE && npx -y @anthropic-ai/claude-code\n```\n\n---\n\n**最快的方法：使用 cmd 命令**，不需要修改任何设置，直接运行即可。"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":246,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":18432,"output_tokens":258,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"8fd8d843-da48-4349-9946-0b417e2c0579","timestamp":"2026-02-25T05:47:24.921Z"}
